<p>Hi {{ greeting_name }},</p>
<p>Your main gap is <strong>{{ top_issue }}</strong>. Quick context: {{ issue_description[:280] }}{% if issue_description|length > 280 %}…{% endif %}</p>
{% if recommended_fix %}<p>Suggested fix (short): {{ recommended_fix[:200] }}{% if recommended_fix|length > 200 %}…{% endif %}</p>{% endif %}
{% if code_snippet %}<p>Here’s a tight copy-paste snippet (trimmed for email):</p>
